<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/Logo-Icon.png" type="image/png">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="ambient-gradient"></div>
  <div class="ambient-diagonal"></div>

  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <section class="landing-hero">
    <p class="arm-eyebrow">ACED Trades · Financial Markets</p>
    <h1>Market Intelligence Built on<br>Discipline, Not Guesswork.</h1>
    <p>Strategy frameworks, risk-aware execution models, and trading systems designed for futures and forex environments where precision is the only acceptable standard.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="#expertise" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Framework</a>
      <a href="#portfolio" class="btn btn-secondary">See Trading Systems</a>
      <a href="mailto:support@aceddivision.com" class="btn btn-accent">Start a Conversation</a>
    </div>
    <div class="capability-strip">
      <div class="capability-strip-inner">
        <span>FOREX TRADING</span><span>·</span>
        <span>FUTURES MARKETS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>RISK MANAGEMENT</span><span>·</span>
        <span>MARKET ANALYSIS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>TRADING SYSTEMS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>STRATEGY COACHING</span><span>·</span>
        <span>EXECUTION FRAMEWORKS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>FOREX TRADING</span><span>·</span>
        <span>FUTURES MARKETS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>RISK MANAGEMENT</span><span>·</span>
        <span>MARKET ANALYSIS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>TRADING SYSTEMS</span><span>·</span>
        <span>STRATEGY COACHING</span><span>·</span>
        <span>EXECUTION FRAMEWORKS</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="trust-strip">
    <div class="trust-item">
      <h3>Multi-Market Experience</h3>
      <p>Forex pairs, futures contracts, and commodity instruments</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <h3>Risk-First Framework</h3>
      <p>Capital preservation is the foundation of every strategy</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <h3>Data-Driven Decisions</h3>
      <p>Every entry, exit, and position size backed by analysis</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="numbered-list" id="expertise">
    <h2>Four things every serious trader knows.</h2>
    <div class="numbered-items">
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">01</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Emotion is the enemy of execution</h3>
          <p>Without a rules-based framework, every decision under pressure is a gamble. The market rewards those who've already decided how they'll act before the candle closes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">02</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Risk management determines longevity</h3>
          <p>A great entry means nothing if position sizing destroys the account on the inevitable losing streak. Consistent profits come from controlled losses, not lucky wins.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">03</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Strategy without backtesting is speculation</h3>
          <p>Trading a setup you've never validated is hope disguised as strategy. Conviction comes from data — how the setup performs across hundreds of occurrences.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="numbered-item">
        <span class="numbered-item-num">04</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Most traders over-trade their account</h3>
          <p>Chasing setups, forcing trades, and holding losers too long — the discipline to sit on hands is often the most profitable skill in a trader's arsenal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section" style="padding-top:0;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom:2rem;">Our trading framework, applied.</h2>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>💱 Forex Strategy Systems</h3>
        <p>Rules-based forex frameworks covering entry criteria, stop placement, take-profit levels, and session-based execution patterns.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>📊 Futures Market Analysis</h3>
        <p>Expert guidance across commodity, index, and interest rate futures — with structured approaches to position management and contract selection.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>⚠️ Risk Management Systems</h3>
        <p>Position sizing models, drawdown rules, and capital allocation frameworks that protect your account and support consistent compounding.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>📈 Technical & Fundamental Analysis</h3>
        <p>In-depth market analysis providing actionable bias and confluences — combining price structure, volume, and macro context.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>🎯 Strategy Coaching</h3>
        <p>Personalised strategy sessions tailored to your trading style, risk tolerance, and capital objectives — with real accountability checkpoints.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-item">
        <h3>⚙️ Algorithmic & Systematic Tools</h3>
        <p>Custom trading utilities and scripts that support systematic execution, screener logic, and rules-based alert systems.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <% if (featuredProjects && featuredProjects.length > 0) { %>
  <section class="showcase" id="portfolio">
    <div class="max-w-container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Trading Systems</p>
      <h2>Tools Built for the Market</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Systematic tools, trading utilities, and market intelligence systems built to give disciplined traders a structural edge.</p>
      <div class="showcase-grid">
        <% featuredProjects.forEach((project) => { %>
          <article class="showcase-card">
            <h3><%= project.title %></h3>
            <p><%= project.description %></p>
            <div class="chip-row">
              <% (project.tags || []).slice(0, 3).forEach((tag) => { %><span><%= tag %></span><% }) %>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top:1rem;">
              <a href="/portfolio/<%= project.slug %>">View case study →</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-buttons" style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <a href="/portfolio?arm=trades" class="btn btn-secondary">View All Trading Work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <% } %>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="features-content">
      <h2>Trading Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Data-Driven</h3>
          <p>Every decision backed by historical analysis, confluences, and validated setups — not instinct.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Risk Conscious</h3>
          <p>Capital preservation comes first. No trade is worth blowing the account for.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Rules-Based Execution</h3>
          <p>A defined playbook for every market condition removes emotion from the equation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <h3>✦ Adaptive Framework</h3>
          <p>Strategies that evolve with changing market structure, volatility regimes, and macro conditions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div style="background:#fff9e6;border:1px solid #f0c239;border-radius:16px;padding:1.8rem 2rem;">
      <h3 style="color:#a16207;margin-bottom:0.6rem;">⚠️ Important Risk Disclosure</h3>
      <p style="color:#92400e;margin:0;font-size:0.95rem;">Trading financial markets involves substantial risk of loss. Past performance is not indicative of future results. All trading strategies carry inherent risks including potential loss of principal. Always conduct your own research and consult a qualified financial advisor before making investment decisions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div>
        <p class="arm-eyebrow">ACED Trades</p>
        <h2>Serious about your trading? Let's talk strategy.</h2>
        <p>Whether you're building consistent execution habits or need a systematic framework, we'll help you develop an approach grounded in data and discipline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-actions">
        <a href="mailto:support@aceddivision.com" class="btn btn-accent">support@aceddivision.com</a>
        <a href="tel:+14709700798" class="btn btn-secondary">470 970 0798</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="arm-footer" id="footer-area">
    <p><strong>ACED Trades</strong> — Financial Markets</p>
    <p>Part of <a href="/">ACED Division LLC</a> · <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    <p style="margin-top:0.8rem;">© 2026 ACED Division LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
